# 📘 PHP Blog REST API

A lightweight **RESTful API built with core PHP (MVC architecture)** for managing blog posts, users, and authentication using JWT.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 JWT Authentication (Login / Register)
- 👤 User Management
- 📝 Blog Post CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
- 💬 Comment System (Add / View comments)
- ❤️ Like System (Like / Unlike posts)
- 🔎 Search posts by title
- 📂 Filter posts by category
- 🛡️ Middleware-based route protection
- ⚡ Clean MVC architecture
- 🧩 Custom Router
- 🗄️ PDO-based database connection (secure & prepared statements)
